&lt;p&gt;National Car Rental and Diners Club International are partnering to provide Diners Club cardmembers complimentary Emerald Club Executive status.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Discover the speed, choice and rewards that set Emerald Club&reg; Executive apart from the rest.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;● SPEED AND CHOICE &ndash; Bypass the counter, choose any car (Fullsize and above) from the Executive Selection area and only pay the reserved Midsize rate.&lt;br /&gt;
● GUARANTEED UPGRADES &ndash; You&amp;#8217;re always guaranteed a free upgrade when you reserve at the Midsize rate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nationalcar.com/en_US/car-rental/partners/partner-details/affinity/5031327-diners-club-international.html&quot;&gt;Click here&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to reserve your rental car!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Terms &amp;amp; Conditions: Discount applies to base rate only. Up to 25% discount applies to participating locations. Discount varies by rental date, location and vehicle type. Taxes other governmentally-authorized or imposed surcharges, license and concession recoupment fees, airport and airport facility fees, fuel, additional driver fee, one-way rental charge and optional items (such as LDW up to US $30 per day) are extra. In the US check your insurance and/or credit card for rental vehicle coverage. Renter must meet standard age, driver and credit requirements. 24-Hour advance reservation required. May not be combined with other discounts. Availability is limited. Subject to change without notice. Blackout dates may apply. Void where prohibited.&lt;/p&gt;
